# System Design Standards

## Architecture
- Modular monolith. Layers: Presentation, Application, Domain, Data, Integration, Platform, Quality.

## Security
- HTTPS, input sanitization, output encoding, CSRF, rate limiting.
- OWASP Top 10. Secure secrets. Encrypted at rest & in transit.

## Quality
- Unit (logic), integration (API+DB), E2E (critical flows).
- CI-triggered tests. Quality gates before merge.

## Observability
- Structured logs (JSON). Correlation IDs.
- Metrics: latency, error rates, resource utilization.

## Scalability
- Stateless services. Horizontal scaling. Database read replicas.
- Graceful degradation. Feature flags.
